headline: Republic Services (NYSE:RSG) Misses Q3 Revenue Estimates
summary: Waste management company Republic Services (NYSE:RSG) fell short of the markets revenue expectations in Q3 CY2025 as sales rose 3.3% year on year to $4.21 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.90 per share was 6.5% above analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: Republic Services, Inc. Reports Third Quarter 2025 Results
summary: Republic Services, Inc. (NYSE: RSG) today reported net income of $550 million, or $1.76 per diluted share, for the three months ended September 30, 2025, versus $566 million, or $1.80 per diluted share, for the comparable 2024 period. Excluding certain expenses and other items, on an adjusted basis, net income for the three months ended September 30, 2025, was $594 million, or $1.90 per diluted share, versus $568 million, or $1.81 per diluted share, for the comparable 2024 period.
